tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE customer_feedback (
    feedback_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name VARCHAR(50),
    feedback_text TEXT,
    date_added TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE review (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  customer_id INT,
  review_text TEXT,
  rating INT,
  date_posted DATE
);

CREATE TABLE customer_reviews (
    review_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT,
    product_id INT,
    review_text TEXT,
    review_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE product_ratings (
    rating_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    product_id INT,
    customer_id INT,
    rating_value INT,
    rating_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE customer_demographics (
    customer_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name TEXT,
    customer_email TEXT,
    customer_age INT,
    customer_gender TEXT
);
